name: # Infinite Frames 01 #
description:
This frame were generated using hydra synth through a live generative code / SVG / JavaScript.

Why frames?

When working with SVG in HEN, navigating your profile can become truly difficult, as the computer tries to read and process everything on the screen at the same time. The # Infinite Frames # collection was created as an attempt to work around this problem, since most of the community doesn't have supercomputers, including me. The launch sequence of each piece will be 1 live generative mint, then 3 of my favorites psychedelic frames of the live generative piece. Most will be free or for gifts, so enjoy! Feel free to collect, but I would like to politely ask each user to limit himself to collecting only 1 edition of each frame, giving opportunity to others.

2864x2864 pixels | PNG
